description:
"A weekend in the nature, in a small group of yogis dedicated to yogic practices such as restorative sequences and yin yoga, mindfulness, guided breath work and meditation so we can quiet the mind and reconnect to our inner resources.
We open the retreat on Friday afternoon with the Circle of Intent and Cacao ceremony, and we end it on Sunday after lunch.
The food is sattvic, fresh, local and vegetarian (vegan on request).
Max 8 people.
For info: sandra@GAIA-YOGA.COM"
name: ReNew: weekend yoga retreat with Sandra D. Bianco
